Two players in each tank
Start with two tanks, ideally up to 16
One player is the gunner/commander, the other is the driver
Commander sits on top of tank and aims and fires the gun
Driver sits within the tank

Easiest gun implementation: 
  Player with a bow
  Bow is unbreakable
  Bow has infinity
  Fired arrows are replaced by fireballs

Map bounds:
 -60 to 60

 121 blocks